Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.66,CN - up,Mai,0,0,0,,庵珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.83,CN,Suguri,0,0,0,,希
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:51.75,CN,Nanase,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:52.67,CN,Anzu,0,0,0,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.92,CN,Nozomi,0,0,0,,下面 在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:57.15,CN,Nozomi,0,0,0,,不行 听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.81,CN,Anzu,0,0,0,,要走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:17.49,CN,Nanase,0,0,0,,多亏了去找希 我的睡眠都不足了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:18.94,CN,Nozomi,0,0,0,,都说了抱歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.26,0:20:22.82,CN,Mai,0,0,0,,但没事就好 希和庵珠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.11,CN,Mai,0,0,0,,还有那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:28.45,CN,Nozomi,0,0,0,,才不好 手机电都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.61,0:20:30.73,CN,Mai,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.43,CN,Nozomi,0,0,0,,怎 怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:44.16,CN,Rina,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:44.97,CN,Nozomi,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:48.60,CN,Rina,0,0,0,,我实际上很开心 你们没有抛下我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:53.10,CN,Nozomi,0,0,0,,我也是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.95,CN,Nozomi,0,0,0,,要一起回去哦
